    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Admin
    Entity class representing an admin user in the system.
    AdminController
    REST controller for managing admins.
    AdminDto
    Data Transfer Object for the Admin entity.
    AdminMapper
    Utility class for mapping between Admin entity and AdminDto.
    AdminRepository
    Repository interface for Admin entities.
    AdminService
    Service interface for managing admins.
    AdminServiceImpl
    Implementation of the AdminService interface.
    EraBackendApplication
    Main application class for the EraHotel backend.
    Guest
    Guest Entity class that represents a Guest obj in the Era Hotel database This stores personal details such as name, email and phone Also stores a List of strings which are reservationId's stored in guestReservations the logic for appending a reservationId into the list is defined in the frontend within BookingForm.jsx
    GuestController
    REST controller for managing guest-related operations in the system privides endpoints for creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting guest records, as well as appending reservation ID's to guests.
    GuestDto
    Data Transfer Object for the Guest entity.
    GuestMapper
    Utility class for mapping between Guest entity and GuestDto.
    GuestRepository
    Repository interface for Guest entities.
    GuestService
    Service interface for managing guests.
    GuestServiceImpl
    Implementation of the GuestService interface.
    Reservation
    Entity class representing a reservation in the system.
    ReservationController
    REST controller for managing reservations.
    ReservationDto
    Data Transfer Object for the Reservation entity.
    ReservationIdGenerator
    Utility class for generating custom reservation IDs.
    ReservationMapper
    Utility class for mapping between Reservation entity and ReservationDto.
    ReservationRepository
    Repository interface for Reservation entities.
    ReservationService
    Service interface for managing reservations.
    ReservationServiceImpl
    Implementation of the ReservationService interface.
    ResourceNotFoundException
     
    Room
    Entity class representing a room in the hotel reservation system.
    RoomController
    REST controller for managing rooms.
    RoomDto
    Data Transfer Object for the Room entity.
    RoomMapper
    Utility class for mapping between Room entity and RoomDto.
    RoomRepository
    Repository interface for Room entities.
    RoomService
    Service interface for managing rooms.
    RoomServiceImpl
    Implementation of the RoomService interface.
